Class ProcessorDynamicState

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.datacenter.data.AbstractTimeStampedData

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.DataOfferedI.DataI, fr.sorbonne_u.components.interfaces.DataRequiredI.DataI, ProcessorDynamicStateI, TimeStampingI, java.io.Serializable

    public class ProcessorDynamicState
extends AbstractTimeStampedData
implements ProcessorDynamicStateI
    The class ProcessorDynamicState implements objects representing a snapshot of the dynamic state of a processor component to be pulled or pushed through the dynamic state data interface.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant              coresIdleStatus != null and currentCoreFrequencies != null
